rdf:Description.ns1:label: Gomphrena
rdf:Description.ns1:abstract: Gomphrena is a genus of plants in the family Amaranthaceae. They are known as the globe amaranths. Species include: * Gomphrena agrestis * Gomphrena canescens * Gomphrena celosioides * Gomphrena globosa—Globe amaranth * Gomphrena haageana—Strawberry globe amaranth * * Gomphrena pohlii * Gomphrena prostrata * * * Gomphrena sonorae
